name: 🅻🅾🅽🅴🅻🅸🅽🅴🆂🆂
description:
Many people do not want to be alone, they want to have people they love around them, and they want to have beautiful moments with those people. Some people voluntarily isolate themselves from society and choose to be on their own, and the weird thing is, they like solitude. 
There are some people, they don't choose loneliness, loneliness chooses those people, people exclude her/his, they don't want to be with her/his
